The paper is about a deep learning model for answer selection in question answering applications. This falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning, which are covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it covers NLP and information retrieval (IR) topics. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories as they cover deep learning and neural network models. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as it covers the task of answer selection. Finally, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category but still relevant as it covers neural network models.
